entities.description: An indicator related to agency activities, such as Blk, GrpAB, Window.
The unweighted frequency of the occurrence of a specific activity indicator.
The month during which the agency activity indicator was measured, such as November or December.
Total number of cases used for measuring the activity indicators.

relationships.description: Relates activity indicators to their respective unweighted frequencies.
Associates a month with its respective agency activity indicators.
Relates a month to the total number of cases for its activity indicators.
